OL,5,G1855 Four in a Bed
OL,6,     FNoorani's declaration that she'd
OL,7,     Fhappily eat off the bathroom
OL,8,     Ffloors at her B&B - The
OL,9,     FCasterbridge in Dorchester -
OL,10,     Fdoesn't ring true for some of her
OL,11,     Fguests.
OL,12,G1925 Four in a Bed
OL,13,     FNancy and her friend Henrietta
OL,14,     Fhost at Nancy's family farmhouse,
OL,15,     FOvertown Manor, in Wiltshire. A
OL,16,     Fcooking experience goes down well,
OL,17,     Fbut plumbing problems throw a
OL,18,     Fspanner in the works.
