OL,5,G1955 Four in a Bed
OL,6,     FThe final visit takes the B&Bers
OL,7,     Fto The Castle Inn in Devon, where
OL,8,     Fhosts Amanda and Josie aim to
OL,9,     Fsweeten their guests with a visit
OL,10,     Fto a local honey manufacturer.
OL,11,G2030 Four in a Bed
OL,12,     FAfter a week of dog poo diatribe,
OL,13,     Fspicy omelettes and farm faux pas,
OL,14,     Fthe B&Bers meet one last time to
OL,15,     Fhave a big old row and find out
OL,16,     Fwho's won.
OL,17,G2100 24 Hours in A&E
OL,18,     FA touching episode about people
OL,19,     Fliving on their own and reaching
OL,20,     Fout to others. Scaffolder Thomas
OL,21,     Fhas been hit on the head by a
OL,22,     Fsix-metre pole on a building site.
