OL,6,     FThis episode focuses on how people
OL,7,     Fdeal with physical and emotional
OL,8,     Fpain. Dad-of-four Simon hasn't
OL,9,     Featen for days after his partner
OL,10,     Fended their relationship.
OL,11,G2305 999: On the Front Line
OL,12,     FParamedics treat a woman who's
OL,13,     Fcollapsed in a bus shelter, a
OL,14,     F90-year-old man who has stabbing
OL,15,     Fpains in his chest and an
OL,16,     F11-month-old with a cut forehead.
